title: The Ancient Magus Bride Episode 6 The Faerie Queen English Dub 1
description:
More than ten days have passed since the incident at Ulthar, but Chise is still in a deep sleep. Elias and Simon stand worriedly by her side, when they are met by unexpected guests.

This is a 1080p Funimation Dubbed Anime Episode of The Ancient Magus Bride Episode 6
